# Industrial Equipment Monitoring System

A real-time industrial monitoring system that collects sensor data from simulated machines, detects anomalies, and visualizes equipment health through a dashboard.

Features

• Real-time sensor ingestion using FastAPI
• Equipment anomaly detection (temperature & vibration)
• Alert generation for abnormal conditions
• Sensor simulator for testing monitoring pipelines
• React dashboard for visualization
• SQLite database for time-series storage

Architecture
Simulator → FastAPI API → Database → React Dashboard
Tech Stack

Backend

FastAPI

SQLAlchemy

SQLite

Frontend

React

Vite

Data Simulation

Python sensor simulator